             was indicted for <rs id="t18270111-95-off529" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18270111-95-off529" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270111-95-off529" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
